{"tid":432101,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日發夢做同一樣野","createTime":"2017-10-11T08:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T13:56:03.000Z","uid":139762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef854822f3c2b71d43587ef5f62432e59d00474","tid":432101,"uid":139762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"我初中既時候鐘意過一個男仔三年<br />\n我地有曖昧過出過街，佢生日仲同我去睇戲<br />\n但最後都係無結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一直都好後悔果時咁怕醜無同佢表白<br />\n<br />\n到而家都有八年九年<br />\n我仲成日夢到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次係夢入面我都係咁追問佢有冇鐘意過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次佢都望住我微笑唔答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底點先可以解開個心結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你見到呢個post可唔可以話我知你到底有冇鐘意過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 而家有個好愛既男朋友 只係唔想再發呢個夢"},{"pid":"bf0c44f0d865a934ce7c43a480cd54614b4f5f37","tid":432101,"uid":87973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T08:22:49.000Z","msg":"最直接咪搵翻果個男仔執翻一劑"},{"pid":"c5c57852d579962bacb1e13cf3b5d5728dcd6af6","tid":432101,"uid":139762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T08:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最直接咪搵翻果個男仔執翻一劑</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好愛我男朋友"},{"pid":"9998301ae2175c5cf81cfdb85962376867ba671d","tid":432101,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0fe2e02b3d5f9fff4fb0b657b3d53cc23fabbf5","tid":432101,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T08:25:40.000Z","msg":"發夢出軌 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臭雞</span></span>"},{"pid":"4bf157062dfb3313e9ac7d8d620b53dbe65516d9","tid":432101,"uid":139762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T08:29:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發夢出軌 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臭雞</span></span></blockquote><br />\n剩係瘋狂問佢同一個問題唔算出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c64a60d211d12cafa9188de6dce34d634dd548","tid":432101,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T08:49:08.000Z","msg":"有一排發夢係咁夢到自己追住同一個男人跑，追極都追唔到<br />\n但係一直望唔到個人係邊個，得個背影"},{"pid":"028b9a714704c8f21d63e599010a8f17e0c7f493","tid":432101,"uid":139762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有一排發夢係咁夢到自己追住同一個男人跑，追極都追唔到<br />\n但係一直望唔到個人係邊個，得個背影</blockquote><br />\n你係咪好想睇佢個樣先追住佢跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d277816f70aa930c1bcf5b44a925a27e733db6","tid":432101,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"點解唔去問"},{"pid":"ab76b2d27329a7c20ca8f084ae6571d537e96f91","tid":432101,"uid":139762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔去問</blockquote><br />\n無聯絡好多年了<br />\n無啦啦走去問又唔係想溝番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好odd"},{"pid":"07becc4a8a66f8736108d6aac9279524d348d30d","tid":432101,"uid":64564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"佢係咪死左報夢比你。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebbea942f27689e725bce0f4acc932cb0f4b98a","tid":432101,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有一排發夢係咁夢到自己追住同一個男人跑，追極都追唔到<br />\n但係一直望唔到個人係邊個，得個背影</blockquote><br />\n你係咪好想睇佢個樣先追住佢跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係，夢入面佢應該係一個好重要嘅人，但個樣好朦朧"}]}